==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''pion'''

#{{physics}} any of three [[semistable]] [[meson]]s, either π<sup>0</sup>, a neutral form with a mass 264 times that of an [[electron]], or π<sup>+</sup> or π<sup>&mdash;</sup>,  a [[charge]]d form with a mass 273 times that of an electron.
#:Note: π<sup>+</sup> is a combination of an [[up quark]] and a [[down antiquark]], π<sup>&mdash;</sup> is a combination of an [[up antiquark]] and a [[down quark]], π<sup>0</sup> is a [[quantum]] mixture of an  [[up quark]], [[up antiquark]] pair and a [[down quark]], [[down antiquark]] pair

